                        Will scraping affect my website's performance? <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        WP ScrapeMaster is optimized for performance. The scraping operations are performed on the server-side and scheduled to run during low-traffic periods, minimizing any impact on your website's performance.
