                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        WP ScrapeMaster is a tool, and like any tool, its legality depends on how you use it. We recommend only scraping content from websites that allow it in their terms of service, or that you have permission to scrape. Always respect copyright laws and intellectual property rights.
